OL,4,Ctraffic scheme scrapped
OL,6,FBob Cruwys talks to Heavitree and
OL,7,FWhipton residents about the scheme
OL,8,Fwhich caused controversy.
OL,10,FBollards and planters are being
OL,11,Fremoved in Exeter after people voted
OL,12,Fagainst a council trial scheme
OL,13,Fdesigned to reduce traffic in
OL,14,Fresidential areas.
OL,16,FCampaigners who fought against the
OL,17,Fcontroversial low traffic
OL,18,Fneighbourhood project were celebrating
OL,19,Fon Monday 1 July, as work began to
OL,20,Ftake away the control measures.
