OL,4,Ctraffic scheme scrapped
OL,6,FDevon County Council introduced the
OL,7,FActive Streets trial in Heavitree and
OL,8,FWhipton in August 2023, to deter rat-
OL,9,Frunning, encourage walking and
OL,10,Fcycling, and reduce pollution.
OL,12,FWithin days of being installed,
OL,13,Fbollards and signs placed to stop
OL,14,Ftraffic were vandalised.
OL,16,FSome residents continued to campaign
OL,17,Fand protest against the scheme, and at
OL,18,Fa review meeting in June this year,
OL,19,Fcouncillors agreed that the trial had
OL,20,Fa 'detrimental effect' and would be
OL,21,Fabandoned.
