OL,6,FOn 1 July, protesters have called the
OL,7,Fremoval of traffic control measures a
OL,8,F"victory for common sense."
OL,10,FLocal resident Clive Hutchings told
OL,11,FITV News West Country: "I've always
OL,12,Fsaid we've got no problem with the
OL,13,Ffact we need to reduce some of the
OL,14,Fjourneys but, as I've always said,
OL,15,Fthese journeys, mostly, are necessary,
OL,16,Fpeople trying to get around to
OL,17,Fhospitals, doctors, schools, whatever.
