OL,6,F"They are not just going out to have a
OL,7,Fbimble, they are trying to get
OL,8,Fsomewhere and you cannot stop people
OL,9,Fdoing that."JDespite the controversy,
OL,10,Fmany people were in favour of the
OL,11,Ftraffic filters.
OL,13,FSupporters say they are disappointed
OL,14,Fthat, for the time being, the roads
OL,15,Fare now going back to how they were
OL,16,Fbefore, because they have really felt
OL,17,Fthe benefits.
