OL,3,CBollards removed after controversial
OL,4,Ctraffic scheme scrapped
OL,6,FResident Nick Gardner said: "It has
OL,7,Fmade an enormous difference outside
OL,8,Four house. You feel safer parking,
OL,9,Fthere is less through traffic, because
OL,10,Feveryone was using that road as a rat
OL,11,Frun and it has increased scooting and
OL,12,Fcycling and walking, people just
OL,13,Fslowing the pace a little bit so for
OL,14,Fpeople that aren't in a huge rush to
OL,15,Fget from A to B it's been absolutely
OL,16,Ffantastic."
